c- tices/essentials 5-web.pdf. UNEP (United Nations Environment Programme). 2002. Urban Issues. Retrieved August 2003 from http://www.unep.or.jp/ietc/Issues/Urban.asp. UNEP (United Nations Environment Programme). 2003. Regional Resource Centre for Asia and the Pacific web- site. Retrieved 2003 from http://www.rrcap.unep.org/ lc/cd/html/countryrep/malaysia/studyarea.html. UNESCO (United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization). 2000. Report of the World Education Forum, Dakar, Senegal, Paris: UNESCO. UNESCO (United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization). 2001.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1c3ffced-fb93-4f82-96b2-28d2d280e10f": {"__data__": {"id_": "1c3ffced-fb93-4f82-96b2-28d2d280e10f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development 2005: Promoting ICT for Human Development in Asia", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "7cea4c72e41d53d8108e013d16e4dfea5b60dbd7ef75a040f8dbf132119e08e1"}, "2": {"node_id": "100a4b79-362f-4dd3-86a8-b4870d052da8", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia", "Author": "United Nations Development Prog