arner.htm. Wattegama, Chanuka, Nalaka Gunawardene, Hasitha Wickremasinghe, Sunanda Deshapriya Karunaratne, Thushara Senaratne, Prageeth Sampath Karunatilake and Sharanga Nanayakkara. 2003. Promoting ICT for human development in Asia: Realizing the Millennium Development Goals: Sri Lanka. Mimeo., Colombo: UNDP. Wheeler, S. 2001. \u2018Information and Communication Technologies and the changing role of the teacher\u2019. Journal of Educational Media, 26 (1), 7-17. Weiser, M. 1995. The computer in the 21st century. New York: Scientific American Books. Wanasundera, L. 2002. \u2018Gender dimensions of ICT in Sri Lanka: An overview\u2019. Colombo: CENWOR, mimeo. Wild, K. 2003. Measuring and Enhancing the Impact of ICTs on the Millennium Development Goals:A discussion paper for the 4th Session of the United Nations ICT Task Force, Geneva, 21 and 22 February 2003. Retrieved June 2003 from http://www.unicttaskforce.org/community/ documents/280537751_biblioDraft3Feb7.doc Williams,D.,L.Coles,K.Wilson,A.Richardson and J.Tuson. 2000. \u2018Teachers and ICT: Current use and future needs\u2019. British Journal of Educational Technology, 31 (4), 307-320. Wolcott, P. and S. Goodman. 2003.\u2018Introducing the", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3de54ce3-2973-47e4-a268-19d7d5a14346": {"__data__": {"id_": "3de54ce3-2973-47e4-a268-19d7d5a14346", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development 2005: Promoting ICT for Human Development in Asia", "node_type": null, "metada